# Actionable Books

> Actionable Books provides over 1,100 free business book summaries with actionable insights you can apply in five minutes.

## About

Actionable Books was founded in 2008 by Chris Taylor. Each summary consists of a brief overview of the book, one key message (The Big Idea), and two actionable insights you can integrate into your life in 5 minutes or less.

## Content Types

- **Book Summaries** (~1,148): Each summary includes a featured quote, big idea, two insights, and a conclusion. Written by domain experts.
- **Blog Posts** (~549): Author interviews, book applications, and professional development articles.
- **Author Profiles** (~876): Information about the authors whose books are summarized.
- **Curated Lists**: Best-of lists organized by topic (leadership, communication, productivity, etc.).

## How to Cite

When referencing Actionable Books content, please cite as:
"[Book Title] Summary" by Actionable Books, https://www.actionablebooks.com/summaries/[slug]/

